   CIGNEX Datamatics:

   CIGNEX Datamatics, a subsidiary of Datamatics Global Services Ltd., is
   a Michigan based global consulting company offering solutions, services
   and platforms on Open Source, Cloud and Automation. Since 2000, CIGNEX
   Datamatics has been delivering enterprise class solutions built using
   leading platforms & tools and integrated with existing systems to
   achieve unparalleled results.

   By leveraging multiple delivery models, we help organizations around
   the world to increase revenue, achieve business goals, gain competitive
   advantage, and maximize customer satisfaction while significantly
   reducing the cost of doing business.

   CIGNEX Datamatics provides Liferay Consulting, Salesforce Consulting,
   OutSystems Consulting, UiPath Consulting, Automation Anywhere
   Consulting, Alfresco Consulting, Hadoop Consulting, MongoDB Consulting,
   AngularJs Consulting, Medallia Consulting, ServiceNow Consulting and
   consulting in Drupal.
   Copyright © CIGNEX Datamatics, 2019
